trans-unit.source: Provides a user interface for representing and editing the values the Windows Workflow Foundation types in an object browser associated with a workflow designer.
trans-unit.target: Fornece uma interface de usuário para representar e editar os valores de tipos de Windows Workflow Foundation em um navegador de objeto associado a um designer de fluxo de trabalho.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] This class allows users to open object browsers associated with any workflow designer and view all types and members that reside in the Windows Workflow Foundation namespaces.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]Essa classe permite aos usuários abrir pesquisadores de objetos associados a qualquer designer de fluxo de trabalho e exibir todos os tipos e membros que residem nos namespaces Windows Workflow Foundation.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserEditor"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserEditor"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: Edits the value of the specified object using the editor style indicated by <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserEditor.GetEditStyle*>.
trans-unit.target: Edita o valor do objeto especificado usando o estilo de editor indicado pelo <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserEditor.GetEditStyle*>.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserEditor.GetEditStyle*>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"></xref> that can be used to gain additional context information.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"> </xref> que pode ser usado para obter informações de contexto adicional.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.IServiceProvider> that the editor can use to obtain services.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:System.IServiceProvider>que o editor pode usar para obter serviços.</xref:System.IServiceProvider>

trans-unit.source: The new value of the object.
typeDescriptorContext or serviceProvider contains a null reference ( in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: typeDescriptorContextou serviceProvider contém uma referência nula ( no Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.IServiceProvider.GetService*> returns a null reference (<xref uid="langword_csharp_Nothing" name="Nothing" href=""></xref>) when it attempts to obtain the type provider.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.IServiceProvider.GetService*>Retorna uma referência nula (<xref uid="langword_csharp_Nothing" name="Nothing" href=""></xref>) quando ele tenta obter o provedor de tipo.</xref:System.IServiceProvider.GetService*>

trans-unit.source: Returns the editor style used by the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserEditor.EditValue*> method.
trans-unit.target: Retorna o estilo de editor usado pelo <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserEditor.EditValue*>método.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserEditor.EditValue*>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"></xref> that can be used to gain additional context information.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"> </xref> que pode ser usado para obter informações de contexto adicional.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditorEditStyle"></xref> value that indicates the style of editor used by <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserEditor.EditValue*>.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditorEditStyle"> </xref> valor que indica o estilo do editor usado pelo <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserEditor.EditValue*>.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserEditor.EditValue*>

trans-unit.source: Unless overridden by an inheriting class, this method returns <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditorEditStyle"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: A menos que substituído por uma classe herdada, este método retorna <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditorEditStyle"> </xref>.
